data.description: Nestled in the heart of Lombard sits this beautiful home. This home offers the perfect combination of comfort and convenience. Step inside to discover an open-concept layout that creates a seamless flow. The updated kitchen is a true highlight, featuring quartz counters, stainless steel appliances, and a convenient coffee station. The impressive laundry room offers functionality and style. With three bedrooms and two bathrooms, everyone has plenty of room. The primary bedroom boasts a custom-built closet system, providing ample storage and optimal organization. The gorgeous updated bathrooms add a touch of luxury to this already stunning home. As you approach the property, you'll notice the new concrete walkway and driveway leading to the 2 1/2-car garage with new door and rafters providing additional storage. The home also offers an expansive sunroom with endless possibilities. Whether you envision it as a relaxing retreat or an entertainment space, this sunroom adds versatility to your lifestyle. This home has been meticulously maintained and updated with today's colors. You'll appreciate the newer lighting, ceiling fans, furnace, doors, and more! Outside, you'll find a fenced backyard with a fire pit and patio, perfect for enjoying those warm summer nights. Just a few blocks from award-winning Pleasant Lane School, Metra, Downtown, Paradise Water Park, The Great Western Trail, and the new library. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own a home in Lombard!
